{"tid":1845412,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"31/1 「廢府·肺話」集會宣布取消","createTime":"2020-01-27T06:56:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T15:50:56.000Z","uid":50306,"like":24,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"1c26dc29a50154e81aae70b2e21d9ae3e8d73cc0","tid":1845412,"uid":50306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T06:56:05.000Z","msg":"親愛的手足，<br />\n鑒於武漢市爆發新型冠狀病毒在港迅速性蔓延，我等團隊以香港市民健康安全為大前提，決定取消於1月31日舉行的 &lt;廢府 &middot; 肺話&gt;集會。<br />\n<br />\n我等在此強烈譴責香港政府，再一次把我們香港人健康推向危險邊緣！<br />\n只為奶共去乞討職位上的利益，而漠視我們的聲音！<br />\n我等團隊支持醫護行列罷工，迫使香港政府盡快落實封關，拒絕這兩個月在中國曾逗留過的任何進出訪客，把疫情盡快控制好，還香港人健康和安心！<br />\n<br />\n此時此刻我們無畏無懼，共同和大家抵抗難關！<br />\n肺炎過後，盼願大家有空出席不同發起渠道的活動，堅持六月反送中開始，手足無間斷響應中共打壓香港民主自由的一切所作所為。<br />\n<br />\n再一次感謝各界手足支持和體諒！<br />\n<br />\n以下係今次眾籌既款項同埋link，望手足互相監察，黎緊我地會繼續搞活動，一日五大訴求未到手，我地都唔會罷撚就<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/「廢府&middot;肺話」集會/#.Xiu1pQiNlU4.whatsapp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%E3%80%8C%E5%BB%A2%E5%BA%9C%C2%B7%E8%82%BA%E8%A9%B1%E3%80%8D%E9%9B%86%E6%9C%83%2F%23.Xiu1pQiNlU4.whatsapp&d=FyFnEhDp3tEmtF3AT420Rgpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=b9c09aca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/「廢府&middot;肺話」集會/#.Xiu1pQiNlU4.whatsapp</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.buymeacoffee.com/sssswingggg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.buymeacoffee.com%2Fsssswingggg&d=FyFnEhDp3tEmtF3AT420Rgpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=bdb01aad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.buymeacoffee.com/sssswingggg</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SDScahn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSDScahn.png&h=90512f03&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iGXGN33.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiGXGN33.png&h=93dfe458&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後都要講返句<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span>"},{"pid":"74682e5bda40c6ba65662c85f442c14440f874a2","tid":1845412,"uid":50306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T07:02:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"407f2768c4b73bcebf57ec6c7c0af761bb28b2dc","tid":1845412,"uid":50306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T07:02:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"da0fe22597c6ea740d9e3c28583e717f940dc0fd","tid":1845412,"uid":23023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T07:02:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6238ba9869a5609703ce8e1986ce6043a5be8f69","tid":1845412,"uid":191812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T07:03:04.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"08da62caf25e7e48d46f931ab9f325405371cedc","tid":1845412,"uid":313341,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T07:03:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5c5945073d7d0f2cc631a36b4215e85de2979cc0","tid":1845412,"uid":314509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T07:04:31.000Z","msg":"幫思穎巴推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bee14590ddf4cc7730fb2506da760aecdb249d8e","tid":1845412,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T07:04:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00209b627d036c4b205af4add5fc8093410cf4f4","tid":1845412,"uid":314509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T07:04:52.000Z","msg":"雖然P牌推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed95fcef339fbd61721a72b61fccd0cb842eff72","tid":1845412,"uid":50306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T07:20:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"532564a60dd6ff63b9abf5098277f9b9887cbfba","tid":1845412,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T07:20:59.000Z","msg":"Objective:<br />\n&gt; Shut down the airline from HK, if Carrie Lam fails to block the 